---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£8Ô∏è‚É£ PRIVACY & DATA PROTECTION BALANCE

While ensuring traceability:

* Sensitive personal data masked when necessary
* Access to personal metadata controlled
* Logs encrypted at rest

Maintains data protection compliance.

---

# 1Ô∏è‚É£9Ô∏è‚É£ COMMON FAILURE POINTS TO AVOID

‚ùå Logs editable by administrators
‚ùå No version tracking
‚ùå No device/IP logging
‚ùå No time synchronization
‚ùå No linkage across modules
‚ùå Log overwriting instead of append-only
‚ùå Audit logs stored in same table as operational data

---

# 2Ô∏è‚É£0Ô∏è‚É£ RISK MITIGATION OUTCOMES

This logic prevents:

* Denial of action
* Covert data manipulation
* Undetected approval bypass
